{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21021.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story07","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":300,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Rika","textCenter":"Darn...","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101}],"textCenter":"I really wanted it to be a surprise, but—"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Ren","nameRight":"Rika","textRight":"Ren..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101}],"textRight":"...Thanks for coming out."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"...Hn..."},{"bg":"bg_adv_21028.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Ren","nameRight":"Rika","textRight":"Here...this is your birthday present.","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302501}],"textLeft":"[chara:302501:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]…!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":200,"mouthOpen":1}],"textRight":"Hey, come on!@Don't stare at it like that!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":1}],"textRight":"I've never done anything like this before,@so I know it's not perfect, but..."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story15","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"It was a lovely little@12-colored pencil set.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21028.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"The case was engraved@with a beautiful drawing@of a lily of the valley..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"(That wasn't fair of her...)","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"After getting something@like this...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21028.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnEffect":"stop"},{"narration":"I know that I can't go@back to how things were."},{"narration":"I'm sorry, but when I think of you,@with your not-so-delicate hands,@engraving something as lovely as this..."},{"narration":"The lily of the valley just blurs@and blurs...and my eyes fill up..."},{"chara":[{"id":302501,"motion":0,"tear":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"...*Sniff*...*Sob*..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":400}],"textRight":"Huh?! Ren?!"},{"chara":[{"id":302501,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"Th-thank you!@Thank you...thank you!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textRight":"…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101}],"textRight":"You're... You're welcome."},{"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"Colored pencils.@Usually I get just one at a time...@When I feel I've helped someone.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21028.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"And here, in just one day,@I'd gotten 12 new colors."},{"narration":"Like always...@She manages to exceed my@every hope with such ease."},{"bg":"bg_adv_11082.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Ren","nameRight":"Rika","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"When you get home, you@should put some ice on them.","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":201}],"textRight":"Your eyes, that is…@They might be swollen tomorrow."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"Oh, yeah..."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story05","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302501}],"textLeft":"Ummm...@I-I'm sorry..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0}],"textRight":"Huh?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"I ummm...@I shouldn't have assumed what I did..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501}],"textLeft":"I just bumped into you at the wrong@time and caused all...all this..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"I'm so ashamed of myself...@I'm so weak..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303101,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":1}],"textRight":"You're not weak.@You're sweet...and pure."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101}],"textRight":"That's why I picked the lily of the valley."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Oh..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0}],"textRight":"Konomi told me about it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303101}],"textRight":"She said the lily of the valley@represents purity."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302501}],"textLeft":"Purity..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101}],"textRight":"Yes.@That's why..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":100}],"textRight":"That's why I thought it was@a perfect match for you, Ren."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"I'm not good at talking to people,@so it's hard for me to understand…","narrationBg":"bg_adv_11082.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"Why is it so easy for everyone else to@come up with the right words?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":100}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"Wow! Look at that!@Isn't the sunset beautiful today?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"Yeah it's very…@Very beautiful."},{"bg":"bg_adv_11022.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"effect":"fadeout","id":302501}],"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"You're always there for me...@Supporting me. But...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_11082.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"I want to change.@I want to be able to tell@you more about myself...@I want you to know me better."},{"narration":"Someday...@When I reach the last page of@this diary, I'll be able to tell you...@About why these pages@are stained with my tears..."},{"narration":"So just a little longer...@Please, just a little more..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Rika","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"Ah! The light's green!@Let's cross!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Ren","textRight":"Okay!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"I know I walk pretty slow, but please...@Please just wait a little longer for me.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_11022.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"Okay, see you tomorrow."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":1}],"textRight":"Yeah...see you tomorrow..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51003_tower_ren/memoria_3025_01.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.2},{"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"There's a special page in@my diary that I like to read@over and over and over again...","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":0.0,"narrationLineSpace":40.0},{"narration":"I talk all about the day I met her in it."},{"narration":"But now I've got a new one.@I've got another page that I'll@want to read over and over."},{"narration":"And naturally, in the corner of that page..."},{"narration":"There's a drawing...@Using 12 colored pencils...@Of a shining lily of the valley."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.2},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51003_tower_ren/memoria_3025_01.jpg","visible":"hide"}]}]},"version":2}